  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Café/Restaurant Service Leader",
  "description": "<p><p><strong>Title: Café/Restaurant Service Leader</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Guide & Inspire Your Crew:</strong> Actively coach, mentor, and motivate the team. Help them grow their skills and confidence every single day.</p></li><li><p><strong>Set the Stage for Excellence:</strong> Uphold our sky-high standards for service, product quality, and spotless cleanliness.</p></li><li><p><strong>Cultivate the Atmosphere:</strong> Foster a warm, professional, and positive vibe on every shift. You set the tone.</p></li><li><p><strong>Master the Experience:</strong> Anticipate guest needs and handle any situation with thoughtful, graceful problem-solving.</p></li><li><p><strong>Keep the Engine Running:</strong> Ensure smooth, efficient, and safe operations during your shifts.</p></li></ul><p><strong>This Role Is For You If:</strong></p><ul><li><p>You light up through human connection and feel deep fulfillment when your team succeeds.</p></li><li><p>You have 1-2 years of experience leading, supervising, or coaching a team. (Café or restaurant experience is a great bonus!)</p></li><li><p>You’re a natural, confident communicator who loves interacting with both guests and team members.</p></li><li><p>You are flexible and available to work a rotating schedule, including weekends.<br /></p><p></p></li></ul></p><p><br /></p><p>EA Personnel R22110043 Tan Eng Kang</p><p>EA License 21C0430 A Dreamworks Company Pte Ltd</p>",
